  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Description\r\n\r\nAfter switching to Light Mode no messages are sent or received at all.\r\n\r\n## Steps to reproduce\r\n1. Launch the app\r\n2. Switch to Light Mode and restart the app\r\n3. Send a message to one of the contacts\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nMessage is delivered to the recipient.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nMessage is not sent.\r\n### Additional Information\r\nFrom the geth.log -> `ERROR[12-20|11:15:54.527|github.com/status-im/status-go/wakuv2/filter_manager.go:355]                        filter resubscribe findPeer error        error=\"filter could not select a suitable peer\"`\r\nNote: After switching back to relay mode all the unsent messages are delivered correctly.\r\n- Status desktop version: StatusIm-Desktop-v0.15.0-rc.9-6dc10b\r\n- Operating System: macOS Sonoma 14.0\r\n\r\n",
